name: Kingfisher
tagline: Positioned on the edge of Specimen Lake it commands views over the Lakes and breathtaking views over Exmoor. If you enjoy wild life you have found the ideal location for a peace and tranquility holiday.
overview_text:
You don't have to be an angler to appreciate the beautiful views from this Lodge. Positioned on the edge of Specimen Lake it commands views over the Lakes and breathtaking views over Exmoor. If you enjoy wild life you have found the ideal location for a peace and tranquility holiday.
             All lodges have smoke detectors, fire extinguishers, fire blankets and all fitted with carbon monoxide gas alarms. The drinking water at South Combe Waters is fresh natural spring water supplied via a bore hole.
features_text:
Bedrooms: One king sized bedroom and two twin bedrooms with single beds.
Kitchen: The kitchen is equipped with electric oven, ceramic hob, microwave and fridge-freezer, and is finished with quality fixtures and fittings.
Dining: There is a dedicated dining area to enjoy a meal with the family, or a romantic dinner.
Lounge: The Lounge area has a comfortable leather sofa and arm chair. The open plan nature combined with generous quantities of genuine light from the patio doors and windows means that the Lodge always feels spacious.
Utilities: Gas and Electricity is inclusive in the Holiday cost.
Smoking: We have a No Smoking rule in all Lodges.
Patio Area: All Lodges have there own patio areas with tables, chairs and barbeques.
Television: LCD Television, Dvd Player and a Playstation games console.
Deposit: A returnable security deposit of £50.00 is required payable on your arrival, we will return the Security Deposit once the property has been inspected at the end of your rental period.
Tackle Shed: All Lodges have there own fishing tackle sheds.
Bathroom: The Bathroom is on the ground floor with a corner bath and an over bath shower.
description: With commanding views stretching for miles over the Devon countryside, Kingfisher Lodge is just a few steps from the main Specimen Lake. Kingfisher Lodge has one King sized room and two twin rooms with two single beds in each, spacious living/dining area, kitchen and bathroom. A perfect lodge for the perfect family holiday.

We require a cash deposit of £50 on arrival to cover any incidental damages and breakages that may occur. This is returned to you on the day you leave once we have inspected the lodges.
